   {2\left( {x - {1 \over 2}} \right)} &amp; {x - 1} &amp; {{x^2}}  \cr 
   1 &amp; 0 &amp; x  \cr 
   x &amp; 1 &amp; 0  \cr 

 } } \right|$$ is equal to :

